---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageNav from "../../components/PageNav.astro";
---

<Layout title="Design System">
    <header class="article-header">
        <h1
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[60px] leading-[0.95] tracking-tight font-bold text-black dark:text-white mb-4 lowercase"
        >
            design system
        </h1>
        <PageNav
            items={[
                { label: "colophon", href: "/colophon" },
                {
                    label: "design system",
                    href: "/colophon/design-system",
                    active: true,
                },
                { label: "políticas", href: "/policy" },
                { label: "changelog", href: "/colophon/changelog" },
            ]}
        />
    </header>

    <div class="article-grid">
        <article class="text-column">
            <div class="section-divider">§</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">01. tipografia</h2>

            <p class="body-text first-paragraph">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. O <em
                    >horror vacui</em
                > é substituído pelo silêncio. Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut
                labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud
                exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip.
            </p>

            <p class="body-text">
                Este é um parágrafo padrão com um <span class="highlight"
                    >destaque tipográfico</span
                > e um <a href="#" style="text-decoration: underline;"
                    >link no corpo do texto</a
                >. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit
                esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.
            </p>

            <figure class="swiss-quote">
                <blockquote>
                    O design não é apenas o que parece e o que se sente. O
                    design é como funciona.
                </blockquote>
                <figcaption>— Steve Jobs (Apócrifo)</figcaption>
            </figure>

            <div class="section-divider">§</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">02. código e sintaxe</h2>

            <div class="code-ide">
                <div class="ide-header">
                    <span class="dot red"></span><span class="dot yellow"
                    ></span><span class="dot green"></span>
                    <span class="filename">exemplo.js</span>
                    <button class="copy-btn">copiar</button>
                </div>
                <pre><code><span class="token selector">function</span> <span class="token func">iniciarSistema</span>() &#123;
  <span class="token selector">const</span> <span class="token prop">estado</span> = <span class="token str">"ativo"</span>;
  <span class="token comment">// O silêncio é calculado</span>
  <span class="token selector">return</span> <span class="token num">42</span>;
&#125;</code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="section-divider">§</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">03. figuras e legendas</h2>

            <figure class="figure-wide">
                <div class="img-wrapper">
                    <img
                        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516961642265-531546e84af2?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop"
                        alt="Arte Abstrata"
                    />
                </div>
                <figcaption class="caption-side">
                    <span class="fig-num">FIG. 1</span> — Exemplo de imagem com breakout
                    (120% de largura) e legenda lateral, preservando a mancha gráfica.
                </figcaption>
            </figure>

            <h3 class="subsection-title">taxonomia semântica</h3>
            <div class="tags-cloud">
                <span class="tag tag-sulfur">conceito puro</span>
                <span class="tag tag-sulfur">ideia</span>
                <span class="tag tag-vermilion">crítico</span>
                <span class="tag tag-gray">histórico</span>
                <span class="tag tag-lavender">tecnologia</span>
                <span class="tag tag-lavender">frontend</span>
            </div>

            <h3 class="subsection-title">lista de projetos</h3>
            <div class="project-list">
                <a href="#" class="project-link">
                    <span class="p-icon bg-ink">a</span>
                    <span class="p-info">
                        <span class="p-name">antigravity</span>
                        <span class="p-desc">sistema de design</span>
                    </span>
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="project-link">
                    <span class="p-icon bg-vermilion">p</span>
                    <span class="p-info">
                        <span class="p-name">paradoxo</span>
                        <span class="p-desc">estudo de caso</span>
                    </span>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="action-area">
                <p class="mono-label">AÇÕES:</p>
                <div class="button-group">
                    <button class="btn-primary">ação principal</button>
                    <button class="btn-ghost">secundária</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section-divider">§</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">04. cores</h2>

            <p class="body-text">
                A paleta de cores é minimalista e funcional, com cores
                semânticas para destaque e feedback.
            </p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-12">
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div
                        class="h-24 bg-black dark:bg-white border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-xs font-mono">
                        <span class="block font-bold">Ink</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-500">--c-ink</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div
                        class="h-24 bg-white dark:bg-black border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-xs font-mono">
                        <span class="block font-bold">Background</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-500">--c-bg</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div class="h-24 bg-[var(--c-vermilion)]"></div>
                    <div class="text-xs font-mono">
                        <span class="block font-bold">Vermilion</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-500">--c-vermilion</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div class="h-24 bg-[var(--c-sulfur)]"></div>
                    <div class="text-xs font-mono">
                        <span class="block font-bold">Sulfur</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-500">--c-sulfur</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div class="h-24 bg-[var(--c-lavender)]"></div>
                    <div class="text-xs font-mono">
                        <span class="block font-bold">Lavender</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-500">--c-lavender</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div class="h-24 bg-neutral-500"></div>
                    <div class="text-xs font-mono">
                        <span class="block font-bold">Gray</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-500">--c-gray</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                    <div class="h-24 bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800"></div>
                    <div class="text-xs font-mono">
                        <span class="block font-bold">Light Gray</span>
                        <span class="text-neutral-500">--c-light-gray</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section-divider">§</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">05. escala tipográfica</h2>

            <div class="space-y-8 mb-12">
                <div
                    class="border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-4"
                >
                    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-neutral-400 block mb-2"
                        >Display Title (H1)</span
                    >
                    <h1
                        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[60px] leading-[0.95] tracking-tight font-bold text-black dark:text-white lowercase"
                    >
                        the quick brown fox
                    </h1>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-4"
                >
                    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-neutral-400 block mb-2"
                        >Section Title (H2)</span
                    >
                    <h2
                        class="text-[30px] leading-[1.1] tracking-tighter font-semibold text-black dark:text-white lowercase"
                    >
                        jumps over the lazy dog
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-4"
                >
                    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-neutral-400 block mb-2"
                        >Subsection Title (H3)</span
                    >
                    <h3
                        class="text-xl font-medium text-neutral-900 dark:text-white lowercase"
                    >
                        pack my box with five dozen liquor jugs
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-4"
                >
                    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-neutral-400 block mb-2"
                        >Body Text</span
                    >
                    <p class="body-text mb-0">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
                        Sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore
                        magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud
                        exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea
                        commodo consequat.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-4"
                >
                    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-neutral-400 block mb-2"
                        >UI Text / Caption</span
                    >
                    <p
                        class="font-sans text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400"
                    >
                        Sphinx of black quartz, judge my vow.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 pb-4"
                >
                    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-neutral-400 block mb-2"
                        >Monospace / Code</span
                    >
                    <p
                        class="font-mono text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400"
                    >
                        const designSystem = "consistent";
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section-divider">§</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">06. espaçamento</h2>

            <div class="space-y-4 mb-12">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-4 h-4 bg-vermilion/20 border border-vermilion"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-mono text-sm">0.25rem (4px) - gap-1</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-8 h-8 bg-vermilion/20 border border-vermilion"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-mono text-sm">0.5rem (8px) - gap-2</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-16 h-16 bg-vermilion/20 border border-vermilion"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-mono text-sm">1rem (16px) - gap-4</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-24 h-24 bg-vermilion/20 border border-vermilion"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-mono text-sm">1.5rem (24px) - gap-6</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-32 h-32 bg-vermilion/20 border border-vermilion"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-mono text-sm">2rem (32px) - gap-8</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section-divider">§</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">07. elementos de ui</h2>

            <h3 class="subsection-title mb-6">botões</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-12">
                <button class="btn-primary"> primary action </button>
                <button class="btn-ghost"> secondary action </button>
                <button
                    class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-200 font-medium border border-transparent"
                >
                    pill button
                </button>
                <button
                    class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 text-neutral-500 hover:text-black dark:hover:text-white transition-colors"
                >
                    outline pill
                </button>
            </div>

            <h3 class="subsection-title mb-6">inputs & forms</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 max-w-md mb-12">
                <div>
                    <label
                        class="block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-2"
                    >
                        text input
                    </label>
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        placeholder="digite algo..."
                        class="w-full bg-transparent border-b border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700 py-2 text-black dark:text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-black dark:focus:border-white transition-colors placeholder:text-neutral-400"
                    />
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label
                        class="block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-2"
                    >
                        select
                    </label>
                    <select
                        class="w-full bg-transparent border-b border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700 py-2 text-black dark:text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-black dark:focus:border-white transition-colors appearance-none rounded-none"
                    >
                        <option>opção 1</option>
                        <option>opção 2</option>
                        <option>opção 3</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <input
                        type="checkbox"
                        id="check1"
                        class="accent-black dark:accent-white w-4 h-4"
                        checked
                    />
                    <label
                        for="check1"
                        class="text-sm text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300"
                        >checkbox selecionado</label
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="subsection-title mb-6">cards</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
                <div
                    class="p-6 bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-lg"
                >
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">card simples</h4>
                    <p
                        class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-4"
                    >
                        Um container básico para agrupar conteúdo relacionado.
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="#"
                        class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:underline"
                        >ler mais →</a
                    >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="group relative flex flex-col gap-3 bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-800/50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-transparent hover:border-neutral-200 dark:hover:border-neutral-700 transition-all"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full aspect-video bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-700 rounded-md mb-1"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-base">card de projeto</h4>
                    <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">
                        descrição curta do projeto.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section-divider">§</div>
            <h2 class="section-title">08. elementos de navegação</h2>

            <p class="body-text">
                A navegação é dividida em três níveis distintos, cada um com sua
                função semântica e visual específica.
            </p>

            <h3 class="subsection-title">submenu de página</h3>
            <p class="body-text">
                Utilizado para navegar entre subpáginas de uma mesma seção (ex:
                Observatório, Escritório). É renderizado pelo componente <code
                    >PageNav</code
                > e aparece logo abaixo do título principal.
            </p>
            <div class="mb-8">
                <PageNav
                    items={[
                        { label: "item ativo", href: "#", active: true },
                        { label: "item inativo", href: "#" },
                        { label: "outro item", href: "#" },
                    ]}
                />
            </div>

            <h3 class="subsection-title">table of contents (toc)</h3>
            <p class="body-text">
                Links de âncora para seções dentro da mesma página (ex:
                Currículo, Políticas). Utiliza o mesmo componente <code
                    >PageNav</code
                >, mas com comportamento de scroll suave.
            </p>
            <div class="mb-8">
                <PageNav
                    items={[
                        { label: "introdução", href: "#intro" },
                        { label: "desenvolvimento", href: "#dev" },
                        { label: "conclusão", href: "#conc" },
                    ]}
                />
            </div>

            <h3 class="subsection-title">filtros dinâmicos</h3>
            <p class="body-text">
                Tags ou botões que filtram o conteúdo exibido na página sem
                recarregá-la (ex: Links, Portfólio). Visualmente distintos,
                geralmente menores ou com contadores.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-2 mb-8">
                <a
                    href="#"
                    class="text-[13px] text-black dark:text-white font-medium transition-colors lowercase whitespace-nowrap"
                >
                    todos
                </a>
                <a
                    href="#"
                    class="group relative flex items-start text-[13px] text-neutral-500 hover:text-black dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors lowercase whitespace-nowrap"
                >
                    categoria a
                    <sup
                        class="text-[9px] text-neutral-300 dark:text-neutral-600 ml-0.5"
                        >05</sup
                    >
                </a>
                <a
                    href="#"
                    class="group relative flex items-start text-[13px] text-neutral-500 hover:text-black dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-white transition-colors lowercase whitespace-nowrap"
                >
                    categoria b
                    <sup
                        class="text-[9px] text-neutral-300 dark:text-neutral-600 ml-0.5"
                        >12</sup
                    >
                </a>
            </div>
        </article>

        <aside class="marginalia-col">
            <div class="sidenote" style="top: 250px;">
                <span class="note-label">NOTA 01</span>
                <p>
                    A capitular ajuda a ancorar o início do texto, criando um
                    ponto focal pesado.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="sidenote" style="top: 600px;">
                <span class="note-label">OBSERVAÇÃO</span>
                <p>
                    As caixas de código simulam um ambiente de IDE, com cores
                    semânticas para facilitar a leitura técnica.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="sidenote" style="top: 1400px;">
                <span class="note-label">CORES</span>
                <p>
                    O sistema de cores prioriza o contraste e a legibilidade,
                    com tons de cinza para estrutura e cores vibrantes para
                    destaque.
                </p>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </div>
</Layout>
